title: Mishimoto Replacement Transmission Oil Cooler Compatible With 2003-2007 Dodge Ram 5.9L Cummins
features: Direct fit for 2003-2007 Dodge Ram 5.9L Cummins
Includes new powdercoated bracket and brass fittings for easy installation
Equivalent to OEM specifications for fit and function
Replaces leaking or failing factory transmission oil cooler
description: Mixing coolant into your transmission fluid can have bad results, and nobody wants to spend thousands of dollars to rebuild or replace their transmission if it can be avoided. The Mishimoto Replacement Transmission Oil Cooler is a direct fit, OEM replacement that requires no modification to install. Made to OEM specifications, this transmission oil cooler is equivalent to an OEM part. By replacing your transmission cooler preventatively, you can save your transmission from falling victim to premature failure. As with all of our products, this cooler is backed by our signature Mishimoto Lifetime Warranty.
